## Data Attribution

The fishing data used in this application is based on historical records from 
Bazaruto waters and is used with permission for educational and research purposes.
The data has been anonymized and aggregated to protect individual privacy.

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for informational and educational purposes only. 
Fishing recommendations are based on historical data analysis and should not 
be considered as professional fishing advice. Users should always:

- Check local fishing regulations and licenses
- Consider current weather and sea conditions  
- Use proper safety equipment and procedures
- Respect marine conservation guidelines
- Fish responsibly and sustainably

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any fishing outcomes,
safety incidents, or regulatory violations that may occur from using this software.
